<h2>About This Application</h2>
<p>
    The <strong>Fitness & Calorie Tracker</strong> is an ASP.NET Core MVC web application designed to help users
    monitor their daily calorie intake, workouts, and progress toward fitness goals.
</p>

<p>
    This project was developed as part of an academic assignment to demonstrate full-stack web development skills,
    including model design, controller logic, and Razor view integration.
</p>

<ul>
    <li>Built with ASP.NET Core MVC</li>
    <li>Uses Entity Framework Core for database management</li>
    <li>Implements CRUD operations for all subsystems</li>
    <li>Provides a clean, Bootstrap-based user interface</li>
</ul>

<a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-secondary">Back to Home</a>
